Travel buddy app were users can create an account, pick a destination, create a post, and write comments on posts.
A User can delete their own post only, and any comments under that post will be deleted regardless of the author.

MODELS

USER
* A user has_many destinations
* A user has_many posts
* A user has_many comments

DESTINATION
* A destination has_many users
* A destination has_many posts

POST
* A post has_many comments
* A post belongs_to a destination
* A post belongs_to a user

COMMENTS
* A comment belongs_to a post
* A comment belongs_to a user
